variables.name: METHOD_OMA_DM
variables.comment:
* OSU (Online Sign-Up) method: OMA DM (Open Mobile Alliance Device Management).
     * For more info, refer to Section 8.3 of the Hotspot 2.0 Release 2 Technical Specification.
     * @hide

variables.name: METHOD_SOAP_XML_SPP
variables.comment:
* OSU (Online Sign-Up) method: SOAP XML SPP (Subscription Provisioning Protocol).
     * For more info, refer to Section 8.4 of the Hotspot 2.0 Release 2 Technical Specification.
     * @hide

variables.name: mOsuSsid
variables.comment: * SSID of the network to connect for service sign-up.

variables.name: mFriendlyNames
variables.comment: * Map of friendly names expressed as different language for the OSU provider.

variables.name: mServerUri
variables.comment: * URI to browse to for service sign-up.

variables.name: mNetworkAccessIdentifier
variables.comment: * Network Access Identifier used for authenticating with the OSU network when OSEN is used.

variables.name: mMethodList
variables.comment: * List of OSU (Online Sign-Up) method supported.

methods.name: public String getFriendlyName()
methods.comment:
* Return the friendly Name for current language from the list of friendly names of OSU
     * provider.
     *
     * The string matching the default locale will be returned if it is found, otherwise the string
     * in english or the first string in the list will be returned if english is not found.
     * A null will be returned if the list is empty.
     *
     * @return String matching the default locale, null otherwise
